    <briefdescription>
<para>This class must be inherited to generate textures of a compatible type with its own renderer. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Ownership:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>It maintains a cache of the loaded textures as a map.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Clearing the cache is safe anytime, as all the created textures are shared pointers and will only be destroyed when all references are lost.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>Guarantees:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Valid textures will be only loaded once.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Cache will priorize loading from the file system.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Deleting a texture or the full cache is safe </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
